headline: Trump Signs Executive Order to Keep TikTok Alive
summary: The order is another step in the effort to keep TikTok running in the U.S., after Congress banned the social media app, under its current Chinese ownership, in 2024.

headline: TrueDialog Promotes Amanda McGuckin Hager to Dual Role of Chief Marketing Officer & Chief Revenue Officer
summary: TrueDialog, a leading provider of enterprise-grade SMS texting solutions, today announced the promotion of Amanda McGuckin Hager to Chief Marketing Officer & Chief Revenue Officer (CMO & CRO). In this expanded role, McGuckin Hager will be responsible for end-to-end revenue strategy and execution, unifying sales, marketing, and partnerships to accelerate growth and deepen customer value.
